title: What is happening with the medical building which was built as part of Autumn Hall on Eastwood Road, across for the Windemere Subdivision? There is a sign out front which says leased, but the building has stayed empty since it was built. The sign has been up for as long as I can remember, but the building appears to be completely empty.
